node.text:
Let’s get this show on the road! We’re here on site at the Red Bull Ring in Spielberg, Austria for the DRM Revival! Here’s the legendary BMW 320 Group 5, driven by Marc Surer. And that’s not all — they’re accompanied by BMW Junior Team members @danharper_, @max.hesse and @neil.verhagen, and the BMW 3.0 CSL!  Jochen Neerpasch, the initiator of the BMW Junior Team of 1977, is also with us to witness the action!

Keep an eye out for more IG stories over the weekend! 

@bmwm @bmwmotorsport @dtm_pics @marc_surer  @redbullring
